{"tid":1322841,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"咪再推梁君彥假文件個post 傳真社follow up過證實佢真係放棄咗英籍","createTime":"2019-07-16T05:16:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T01:01:45.000Z","uid":1065,"like":66,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"bfe363b8417fb89c915e49113fc84258c5dee595","tid":1322841,"uid":1065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T05:16:59.000Z","msg":"好多人淨係睇完標題同樓主條link就盲推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又唔追post 其實入面已經有巴打貼咗link話幾年前已經有查過<br />\n咪撚再推喇 focus返五大訴求啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【採訪手記】傳真社援引英國《資訊自由法》調查梁君彥棄英籍疑團<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.factwire.org/investigation/%E5%82%B3%E7%9C%9F%E7%A4%BE%E6%8F%B4%E5%BC%95%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E3%80%8A%E8%B3%87%E8%A8%8A%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E6%B3%95%E3%80%8B%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5%E6%A2%81%E5%90%9B%E5%BD%A5%E6%A3%84%E8%8B%B1%E7%B1%8D/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.factwire.org%2Finvestigation%2F%25E5%2582%25B3%25E7%259C%259F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%258F%25B4%25E5%25BC%2595%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%259C%258B%25E3%2580%258A%25E8%25B3%2587%25E8%25A8%258A%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%2594%25B1%25E6%25B3%2595%25E3%2580%258B%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E6%259F%25A5%25E6%25A2%2581%25E5%2590%259B%25E5%25BD%25A5%25E6%25A3%2584%25E8%258B%25B1%25E7%25B1%258D%2F&d=SZ2g%2FZg1uDubc4iNJejiXlLn0p5rLcPQxw7X33U7JQw%3D&h=2bbf513e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.factwire.org/investigation/%E5%82%B3%E7%9C%9F%E7%A4%BE%E6%8F%B4%E5%BC%95%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E3%80%8A%E8%B3%87%E8%A8%8A%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E6%B3%95%E3%80%8B%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5%E6%A2%81%E5%90%9B%E5%BD%A5%E6%A3%84%E8%8B%B1%E7%B1%8D/</a><br />\n<br />\n傳真社比對內政部提供的蓋章樣式與10月12日梁君彥展示的《聲明》，發現兩者的蓋章在款式和字型上相符。按署方提供的定義，梁君彥於去年9月22日申請棄籍及於9月30日獲批准，個案歷時8日獲批准。"},{"pid":"9c0cb9a26d0e47d24d59f4ad7faefd14a774b02a","tid":1322841,"uid":1065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T05:17:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e776e325e4e3bcf6508e948fce3e353ab98bfb